_:Nad07da0c7f8c4dc0ae18fc29fbb1edf7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Stuart Anderson was Vice Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) from 14 November 2023 to 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) from 16 February 2023 to 14 November 2023 and Assistant Government Whip from 8 July 2022 to 16 February 2023.</p>\n" .
